From: Jiansong Chen <Jiansong.Chen@amd.com>
Date: Mon, 24 Feb 2020 14:28:34 +0800
Subject: drm/amdgpu: add virtual display support for navy_flounder.
Git-commit: 5404f073595a0fe1edd78d1dadb486fa5eb5c8f2
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

Virtual display support for bring up and virtualization.

Signed-off-by: Jiansong Chen <Jiansong.Chen@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Tao Zhou <tao.zhou1@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
index c8e68de43b12..761cbb72bdfa 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
@@ -527,6 +527,8 @@ int nv_set_ip_blocks(struct amdgpu_device *adev)
 		amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &nv_common_ip_block);
 		amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &gmc_v10_0_ip_block);
 		amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &navi10_ih_ip_block);
+		if (adev->enable_virtual_display || amdgpu_sriov_vf(adev))
+			amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &dce_virtual_ip_block);
 		amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &gfx_v10_0_ip_block);
 		amdgpu_device_ip_block_add(adev, &sdma_v5_2_ip_block);
 		break;
